The '''Undercity Access Pod''' was a vehicle used to traverse the [[Undercity (Peekoine)|Undercity]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Peekoine]] when "[[Slider]]s" were not acceptable. They had the same general statistics as a standard [[Storm IV Twin-Pod cloud car/Legends|Cloud Car]], but were equipped with only repair lasers instead of the Cloud Car's more powerful weaponry. Some of these were used by a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] when they were chasing [[Gamusha]] and his [[Swoop gang/Legends|swoop gang]] [[the Gutterwipes]] in order to rescue [[Plum Tantrellius]] whom they had kidnapped.

